{"tid":1470840,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「要學藍絲」香港地已post道歉中 唔講岩唔岩先係岩","createTime":"2019-08-14T06:49:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T07:41:45.000Z","uid":218552,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3bb6f2bc3d3a68a5470a84e10fdb24b74b868fde","tid":1470840,"uid":218552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:49:39.000Z","msg":"點解建制可以咁硬淨？<br />\n因為出左何妖蔣芸都無屌無罵<br />\n一致對外<br />\n事情已發生 各有各做<br />\n你打人 好 發生左<br />\n你道歉 好 發生左<br />\n屌黎屌執只係哂時間<br />\n文宣有文宣做<br />\n勇武有勇武做<br />\n大家望一望 眼神心照 大家都明都係想成功啫<br />\n跟你自己覺得會成功既方法做 就岩 <br />\n散水 想你安全<br />\n唔散想守 都有佢道理<br />\n呢一刻 唔再屌 唔再罵琴日點 前日點 <br />\n你又點佢又點<br />\n先係各有各做既精神<br />\n放下啦<br />\n8.18 加油<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DN59hRa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDN59hRa.png&h=6a25e0eb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"efcd15a18adfa2e794c4865cb433828c246a498f","tid":1470840,"uid":218552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:53:30.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"b51ab78e354605cec2734fc5c3aa689cc7642c0a","tid":1470840,"uid":218552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:53:47.000Z","msg":"唔好再罵交啦"},{"pid":"9ae37ceac1f45e712ea379d45efdc33b67ffdd1f","tid":1470840,"uid":218552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:54:05.000Z","msg":"唔好嘈啦"},{"pid":"bc98c74cef15da603eba7b08308af5b6efa06e92","tid":1470840,"uid":218552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:54:21.000Z","msg":"乖啦"},{"pid":"961b6741640abaae17e3c187ba6d9ecde1419250","tid":1470840,"uid":11143,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:55:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"95498a61506c588cfd8e5141b21c402f92467bd6","tid":1470840,"uid":218552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:55:10.000Z","msg":"團結呀香港人"},{"pid":"df325ff7a9430fc093ce387ff44b7ec0cf332e01","tid":1470840,"uid":283179,"like":1,"dislike":0